            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>gluten free spaghetti</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked spaghetti</strong> and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-1705423699511-x200.jpg",
