    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>vegetable stock </strong>and <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>to the pan with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 3 min or until the sauce has started to thicken</p><p>Once slightly thickened, add the <strong>drained lentils </strong>and <strong>chopped olives </strong>and cook for a further 3-4 min or until the lentils have slightly softened</p>",
